#spiderhumor

Thought of only using the panel on the right, but I thought the circumstances (driving down a slope towards a bus in a car whose brakes have been damaged by the Liberty’s Torch, which is lending to the car’s velocity with its weight. In California.) were just as important as the joke itself.
